{"lineNumber":183318,"originalJapaneseLine":"……","translatedEnglishLine":"..."},

{"lineNumber":183319,"originalJapaneseLine":"目をギラギラと輝かせた魔物兵達は、","translatedEnglishLine":"The monster soldiers, their eyes gleaming fiercely,"},

{"lineNumber":183320,"originalJapaneseLine":"魔王である来水美樹の捜索を","translatedEnglishLine":"redoubled their efforts in searching for Miki Kousui, the Demon Lord."},

{"lineNumber":183321,"originalJapaneseLine":"より張り切るようになった。","translatedEnglishLine":"They became more and more enthusiastic."},

{"lineNumber":183322,"originalJapaneseLine":"「やりましたねランス様。","translatedEnglishLine":"We did it, Lord Rance."},

{"lineNumber":183323,"originalJapaneseLine":"　勲章が三つ揃いましたよ」","translatedEnglishLine":"We have gathered all three medals."},

{"lineNumber":183324,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……それはいいが","translatedEnglishLine":"...That's fine, but"},

{"lineNumber":183325,"originalJapaneseLine":"　これってなんの役に立つんだ？」","translatedEnglishLine":"what good are these?"},

{"lineNumber":183326,"originalJapaneseLine":"「さ、さあ……？」","translatedEnglishLine":"W-well...?"},

{"lineNumber":183327,"originalJapaneseLine":"「なんだとー？」","translatedEnglishLine":"What did you say?!"},

{"lineNumber":183328,"originalJapaneseLine":"「やーやー、暴力はいかんよ君ー」","translatedEnglishLine":"Hey hey, violence isn't good, you know—"},

{"lineNumber":183329,"originalJapaneseLine":"「私が教えるから抑えて抑えて」","translatedEnglishLine":"I'll explain it, so calm down, calm down."},

{"lineNumber":183330,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あ、ランス様。","translatedEnglishLine":"Ah, Lord Rance."},

{"lineNumber":183331,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ハニーさんが教えて下さるようですよ」","translatedEnglishLine":"Honey-san is going to teach you."},

{"lineNumber":183332,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ふん、じゃあ説明してみろ」","translatedEnglishLine":"Hmph, then try explaining it."},

{"lineNumber":183333,"originalJapaneseLine":"「勲章とは部隊ランクを上げるのに","translatedEnglishLine":"Medals are necessary to raise the unit's rank—"},

{"lineNumber":183334,"originalJapaneseLine":"　必要なものなのだよー」","translatedEnglishLine":"That's what they are."},

{"lineNumber":183335,"originalJapaneseLine":"「部隊ランク？　が上がるとどうなる」","translatedEnglishLine":"Unit rank? What happens when it rises?"},

{"lineNumber":183336,"originalJapaneseLine":"「戦いにとても役立つ","translatedEnglishLine":"You can choose a 'unit bonus' that is very useful in battle."},

{"lineNumber":183337,"originalJapaneseLine":"　『部隊ボーナス』が一つ選べるんだ」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Unit bonus', you get to pick one."},

{"lineNumber":183338,"originalJapaneseLine":"「『部隊ボーナス』は本当にとっても強力。","translatedEnglishLine":"'Unit bonuses' are truly very powerful."},

{"lineNumber":183339,"originalJapaneseLine":"　出来るだけ集めた方がいいよー」","translatedEnglishLine":"You should gather as many as possible."},

{"lineNumber":183340,"originalJapaneseLine":"「なるほど、そういうものなのか」","translatedEnglishLine":"I see, so that's what they are."},

{"lineNumber":183341,"originalJapaneseLine":"「そーそー、そういうものなの」","translatedEnglishLine":"Yes, that's exactly it."},

{"lineNumber":183342,"originalJapaneseLine":"「僕の話、役に立った？」","translatedEnglishLine":"Did my explanation help?"},

{"lineNumber":183343,"originalJapaneseLine":"「はい、とっても」","translatedEnglishLine":"Yes, very much."},

{"lineNumber":183344,"originalJapaneseLine":"「だがお前の偉そうな態度が気に食わん」","translatedEnglishLine":"But I don't like your arrogant attitude."},

{"lineNumber":183345,"originalJapaneseLine":"「割る」","translatedEnglishLine":"Smash!"},

{"lineNumber":183346,"originalJapaneseLine":"「きゃー、やめてー」","translatedEnglishLine":"Kyaa, stop!"},

{"lineNumber":183347,"originalJapaneseLine":"ハニーはぴゃっと逃げ出した。","translatedEnglishLine":"Honey quickly ran away."},

{"lineNumber":183348,"originalJapaneseLine":"「と、とにかく勲章は沢山あるほど","translatedEnglishLine":"A-anyway, the more medals you have,"},

{"lineNumber":183349,"originalJapaneseLine":"　お得みたいなので出来るだけ集めましょう」","translatedEnglishLine":"the better it seems, so let's collect as many as possible."},

{"lineNumber":183350,"originalJapaneseLine":"「そうだな」","translatedEnglishLine":"That's right."}]}

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 見つけたらすぐに離れてケイブリス様に
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Once you find it, immediately retreat and report to Lord Caveblis.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 報告すればいい」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You just need to report.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それだけで……くくく……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Just that alone... hehehe...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ケイブリス様がどれだけ喜ばれるか……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Imagine how delighted Lord Caveblis will be...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「略奪で得られるものなんて
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Don't you think what you gain from plunder...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: たかが知れているとは思わんか？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...is only so much?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「だが、ケイブリス様が魔王になった時……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: But when Lord Caveblis becomes the Demon Lord...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺らに与えられる褒美を想像してみろ……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Imagine the rewards that will be given to us...
Oh...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お、おおおおおおっ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: O-Ohhhh!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そりゃすごい！　すごいっすよ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That’s amazing! Truly amazing!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王から直接褒美が貰えるなんて！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: To receive rewards directly from the Demon Lord!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ふふふ！　そういうことだ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hehe! That's exactly it!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 目も眩むような褒美がもらえるぞ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You'll get dazzling rewards that'll make you dizzy!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「俺なんて夢の魔物将軍にしてもらったり……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I could even become the dream Monster General...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「いや、もしかしたら
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: No, maybe even...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あの魔人にだってしてもらえるかも……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That Demon Beast might even appoint me...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お、俺……奴隷女百人とか欲しいなぁ……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I, I want like a hundred slave women...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「へへ、街の一つくらいだったら
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hehe, maybe they'd even let me control a town or two...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 支配させてくれるかもしんねぇな……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They might let me govern it...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うおおお！　たまんねぇえええ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Wooaah! This is incredibleeee!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 早く早く見つけてやりましょうぜ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Let's find it quickly, quickly!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ふっ、現金な奴らめ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Heh, such mercenary guys.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「俺達以外にも魔王捜索の部隊はいるんだ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There are other teams searching for the Demon Lord besides us!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 遅れるなよ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Don't fall behind!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うおおおおおおおお〜！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Wooooaaaaahhhhhh~!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 目をギラギラと輝かせた魔物兵達は、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The monster soldiers, their eyes gleaming fiercely,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王である来水美樹の捜索を
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: redoubled their efforts in searching for Miki Kousui, the Demon Lord.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: より張り切るようになった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They became more and more enthusiastic.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「やりましたねランス様。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We did it, Lord Rance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 勲章が三つ揃いましたよ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We have gathered all three medals.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……それはいいが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...That's fine, but

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: これってなんの役に立つんだ？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: what good are these?
W-well...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なんだとー？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What did you say?!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「やーやー、暴力はいかんよ君ー」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hey hey, violence isn't good, you know—

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「私が教えるから抑えて抑えて」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'll explain it, so calm down, calm down.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あ、ランス様。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, Lord Rance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ハニーさんが教えて下さるようですよ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Honey-san is going to teach you.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ふん、じゃあ説明してみろ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmph, then try explaining it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「勲章とは部隊ランクを上げるのに
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Medals are necessary to raise the unit's rank—

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 必要なものなのだよー」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's what they are.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「部隊ランク？　が上がるとどうなる」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Unit rank? What happens when it rises?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「戦いにとても役立つ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You can choose a 'unit bonus' that is very useful in battle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 『部隊ボーナス』が一つ選べるんだ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'Unit bonus', you get to pick one.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「『部隊ボーナス』は本当にとっても強力。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'Unit bonuses' are truly very powerful.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 出来るだけ集めた方がいいよー」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You should gather as many as possible.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なるほど、そういうものなのか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I see, so that's what they are.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そーそー、そういうものなの」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yes, that's exactly it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「僕の話、役に立った？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Did my explanation help?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「はい、とっても」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yes, very much.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「だがお前の偉そうな態度が気に食わん」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: But I don't like your arrogant attitude.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「割る」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Smash!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「きゃー、やめてー」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kyaa, stop!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ハニーはぴゃっと逃げ出した。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Honey quickly ran away.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「と、とにかく勲章は沢山あるほど
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A-anyway, the more medals you have,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: お得みたいなので出来るだけ集めましょう」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: the better it seems, so let's collect as many as possible.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そうだな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's right.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「俺なんて夢の魔物将軍にしてもらったり……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I could even become the dream Monster General...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「いや、もしかしたら
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: No, maybe even...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あの魔人にだってしてもらえるかも……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That Demon Beast might even appoint me...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お、俺……奴隷女百人とか欲しいなぁ……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I, I want like a hundred slave women...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「へへ、街の一つくらいだったら
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hehe, maybe they'd even let me control a town or two...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 支配させてくれるかもしんねぇな……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They might let me govern it...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うおおお！　たまんねぇえええ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Wooaah! This is incredibleeee!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 早く早く見つけてやりましょうぜ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Let's find it quickly, quickly!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ふっ、現金な奴らめ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Heh, such mercenary guys.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「俺達以外にも魔王捜索の部隊はいるんだ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There are other teams searching for the Demon Lord besides us!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 遅れるなよ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Don't fall behind!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うおおおおおおおお〜！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Wooooaaaaahhhhhh~!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 目をギラギラと輝かせた魔物兵達は、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The monster soldiers, their eyes gleaming fiercely,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王である来水美樹の捜索を
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: redoubled their efforts in searching for Miki Kousui, the Demon Lord.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: より張り切るようになった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They became more and more enthusiastic.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「やりましたねランス様。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We did it, Lord Rance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 勲章が三つ揃いましたよ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We have gathered all three medals.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……それはいいが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...That's fine, but

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: これってなんの役に立つんだ？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: what good are these?
W-well...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なんだとー？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What did you say?!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「やーやー、暴力はいかんよ君ー」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hey hey, violence isn't good, you know—

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「私が教えるから抑えて抑えて」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'll explain it, so calm down, calm down.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あ、ランス様。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, Lord Rance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ハニーさんが教えて下さるようですよ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Honey-san is going to teach you.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ふん、じゃあ説明してみろ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmph, then try explaining it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「勲章とは部隊ランクを上げるのに
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Medals are necessary to raise the unit's rank—

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 必要なものなのだよー」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's what they are.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「部隊ランク？　が上がるとどうなる」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Unit rank? What happens when it rises?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「戦いにとても役立つ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You can choose a 'unit bonus' that is very useful in battle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 『部隊ボーナス』が一つ選べるんだ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'Unit bonus', you get to pick one.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「『部隊ボーナス』は本当にとっても強力。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'Unit bonuses' are truly very powerful.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 出来るだけ集めた方がいいよー」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You should gather as many as possible.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なるほど、そういうものなのか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I see, so that's what they are.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そーそー、そういうものなの」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yes, that's exactly it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「僕の話、役に立った？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Did my explanation help?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「はい、とっても」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yes, very much.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「だがお前の偉そうな態度が気に食わん」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: But I don't like your arrogant attitude.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「割る」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Smash!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「きゃー、やめてー」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kyaa, stop!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ハニーはぴゃっと逃げ出した。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Honey quickly ran away.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「と、とにかく勲章は沢山あるほど
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A-anyway, the more medals you have,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: お得みたいなので出来るだけ集めましょう」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: the better it seems, so let's collect as many as possible.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そうだな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's right.
